{"tid":30410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【企鵝仔遇溺】七隻企鵝齊齊浸死 專家︰聞所未聞","createTime":"2016-12-09T07:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T10:46:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7dce4f6e667e846596bd5a90da84c04669b9a9a4","tid":30410,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161209/large/1481253846_4232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161209%2Flarge%2F1481253846_4232.jpg&h=ce1b098c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大卡爾加里動物園（Calgary zoo）周四早上有7隻漢波德企鵝（Humboldt penguin，又稱洪堡氏企鵝）難奇溺斃，園方已就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n7隻企鵝是在展館後方區域死亡，園方表示：「我們的企鵝飼養員今早如常工作，不幸地發現一隻企鵝在池中死亡，然後又見到幾隻企鵝在池中死亡，相當震驚。」獸醫為7隻企鵝驗屍，確認牠們死因是溺斃。園方續道：「企鵝是海洋動物，牠們花很多時間在海洋中。事實上漢波德企鵝會外出捕魚長達數周，就待在廣闊的海洋中。」<br />\n<br />\n園方正就事件展開調查，包括翻看出入口的閉路電視片段，園方表示：「似乎一些壓力因素令這些企鵝進入某種恐慌狀態&hellip;&hellip;但難說是甚麼誘發這個情況。」漢波德園區內共有22隻企鵝，仍然生還的並無異常表現。<br />\n<br />\n監察動物園組織「Zoocheck Canada」執行總監萊德勞（Rob Laidlaw）表示：「這事似乎有點神秘。我真的不能想像&hellip;&hellip;我們從未聽過7隻水生鳥類例如企鵝會浸死。」"},{"pid":"b1bb1c24091cfabffd1cf97ea5d4247d4acab34b","tid":30410,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩徵兆？"},{"pid":"15b574596296b9b366b3f1dde28e4ba9bae7a2e0","tid":30410,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:36:54.000Z","msg":"光明會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f895b2b228574c79a5546d40d682a57d7616450","tid":30410,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"2+0+1+2=2012<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bb5a17954798b298df55be89ba8d11addc1bb2","tid":30410,"uid":2121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ebc1230c67ff8499448d9656874f437430ce45","tid":30410,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"壓力因素 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a226497f68144ff685239cbb84da61918c346125","tid":30410,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"今日12月9號<br />\n<br />\n9+1-2=8 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd0699707f6bc011e897dc7b1594c5d83cf2adb","tid":30410,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2+0+1+2=2012<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家2016啦<img src=\"/assets